Before running Mixmaster 3.1 install vim
and put 'export MIXPATH=~/Mix' in your .bashrc.

Copy libcrypto.so.1.0.0 to /usr/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/.

Copy libncurses.so.5, libpcre.so.3 and libinfo.so.5 to
/lib/x86_64-linux-gnu/.

Copy mixmaster to /usr/local/bin/

After that put allpingers.txt in your Mix folder.

P.S. all the files where copied to a Whonix
Workstation and Mixmaster 3.1 works fine there.
